      "text": [
        " رَسُولُ اَللَّهِ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"اِدْرَءُوا اَلْحُدُودَ بِالشُّبُهَاتِ وَ لاَ شَفَاعَةَ وَ لاَ كَفَالَةَ وَ لاَ يَمِينَ فِي حَدٍّ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5146 - The Messenger of Allah (swt) (peace be upon him and his family) said:\n\"Avert prescribed punishments through doubts. There is no intercession, no guarantee, and no oath in matters of prescribed punishments.\""
        ]
      }
